OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776453069
OL,3,CPressure on emergency departments 'is
OL,4,Ccomplex problem with no quick fix'
OL,6,FDeaths associated with waiting in
OL,7,Femergency departments in Northern
OL,8,FIreland have more than doubled in 5
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FNew figures from the Royal College of
OL,12,FEmergency Medicine show there were
OL,13,Fmore than a thousand deaths in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland last year, wihch
OL,15,Fequate to a staggering 20 people a
OL,16,Fweek.
OL,18,FThe Department of Health acknowledged
OL,19,Fthat emergency departments remain
OL,20,Funder significant pressure.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
