FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776453069
OL,3,CPressure on emergency departments 'is
OL,4,Ccomplex problem with no quick fix'
OL,6,FDepartment of Health spokesperson said
OL,7,Fin a statement, "Adding reducing
OL,8,Fdemand and improving patient flow are
OL,9,Fkey, including getting people
OL,10,Fdischarged more quickly," but warned
OL,11,Fprogress will take time because of a
OL,12,Fvery difficult financial position.
OL,14,FShe added, "This is a complex problem
OL,15,Fwith no quick fix but the only medium
OL,16,Fto long term solution is to reduce
OL,17,Fdemand and manage demand differently.
OL,26,@vD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776453069
OL,3,CPressure on emergency departments 'is
OL,4,Ccomplex problem with no quick fix'
OL,6,F"That means reducing the number of
OL,7,Fpeople coming through ED doors as well
OL,8,Fas getting people out of hospital as
OL,9,Fsoon as they are fit for discharge to
OL,10,Ffree up beds.
OL,12,F"Our Reset Plan is attempting, over
OL,13,Fthe next three years, to refocus our
OL,14,Fwork towards earlier support and
OL,15,Fintervention, prevention, providing
OL,16,Fneighbourhood-based care and
OL,17,Fencouraging people to take more
OL,18,Fresponsibility for their own health on
OL,19,Fa routine basis.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776453069
OL,3,CPressure on emergency departments 'is
OL,4,Ccomplex problem with no quick fix'
OL,6,F"We are also looking at how we can
OL,7,Fcare for our frail elderly patients
OL,8,Fbetter by providing more care closer
OL,9,Fto home and preventing avoidable
OL,10,Fadmissions to hospital.
OL,12,F"However, we recognise that this will
OL,13,Ftake time to have an impact and it is
OL,14,Fnot helped by the very challenging
OL,15,Ffinancial position. In the interim, we
OL,16,Fwill continue to manage the quality of
OL,17,Fcare we are able to provide to the
OL,18,Fbest effect ensuring the needs of our
OL,19,Fpatients and staff remain our priority.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
