PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1776453069
OL,3,CPressure on emergency departments 'is
OL,4,Ccomplex problem with no quick fix'
OL,6,F"The Minister has discussed patient
OL,7,Fflow and hospital discharge issues
OL,8,Fwith HSC Chief Executives, and all
OL,9,Fagreed the need to increase community
OL,10,Fcapacity was the most important single
OL,11,Fchange that is required.
OL,13,FThis is consistent with the Reset plan
OL,14,Ftowards a neighbourhood model of
OL,15,Fdelivery."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,18,FITVX
OL,20,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,21,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
